OL,5,Cin Gaza
OL,7,FThe UN's top court says Israel must
OL,8,Ftake "all steps" to prevent genocide,
OL,9,FITV News' John Irvine explains what
OL,10,Fthis ruling means
OL,12,FIsrael must take "all measures in its
OL,13,Fpower" to prevent genocide in Gaza,
OL,14,Fthe International Court of Justice
OL,15,F(ICJ) ruled in an early-stage hearing
OL,16,Fin The Hague on Friday.
OL,18,FIt also recommended that everything
OL,19,Fpossible was done to secure the
OL,20,Fimmediate and unconditional release of
OL,21,Fhostages.
