OL,7,FThe court ruling also referred to the
OL,8,Fpossibility of the living conditions
OL,9,Fin Gaza worsening further, such as the
OL,10,Fspread of epidemic diseases and the
OL,11,Fmass displacement of residents into
OL,12,Fneighbouring countries.
OL,14,FIsrael has to submit a report on the
OL,15,Fallegations outlined in the case
OL,16,Fwithin the next month.
OL,18,FThe court said it would not throw out
OL,19,Fthe genocide case, as requested by
OL,20,FIsrael, after it vehemently rejected
OL,21,Fthe accusation.
